{"ja439:0.1":"Jataka ","ja439:0.2":"Dasakanipata ","ja439:0.3":"Catudvaravagga ","ja439:0.4":"1. Catudvarajataka ","ja439:1.1":"“Catudvaramidam nagaram, ","ja439:1.2":"ayasam dalhapakaram; ","ja439:1.3":"Oruddhapatiruddhosmi, ","ja439:1.4":"kim papam pakatam maya”. ","ja439:2.1":"“Sabbe apihita dvara, ","ja439:2.2":"oruddhosmi yatha dijo; ","ja439:2.3":"Kimadhikaranam yakkha, ","ja439:2.4":"cakkabhinihato aham. ","ja439:3.1":"Laddha satasahassani, ","ja439:3.2":"atirekani visati; ","ja439:3.3":"Anukampakanam natinam, ","ja439:3.4":"vacanam samma nakari. ","ja439:4.1":"Langhim samuddam pakkhandi, ","ja439:4.2":"sagaram appasiddhikam; ","ja439:4.3":"Catubbhi atthajjhagama, ","ja439:4.4":"atthahipi ca solasa. ","ja439:5.1":"Solasahi ca battimsa, ","ja439:5.2":"atriccham cakkamasado; ","ja439:5.3":"Icchahatassa posassa, ","ja439:5.4":"cakkam bhamati matthake. ","ja439:6.1":"Uparivisala duppura, ","ja439:6.2":"iccha visatagamini; ","ja439:6.3":"Ye ca tam anugijjhanti, ","ja439:6.4":"te honti cakkadharino. ","ja439:7.1":"Bahubhandam avahaya, ","ja439:7.2":"maggam appativekkhiya; ","ja439:7.3":"Yesancetam asankhatam, ","ja439:7.4":"te honti cakkadharino. ","ja439:8.1":"Kammam samekkhe vipulanca bhogam, ","ja439:8.2":"Iccham na seveyya anatthasamhitam; ","ja439:8.3":"Kareyya vakyam anukampakanam, ","ja439:8.4":"Tam tadisam nativatteyya cakkam”. ","ja439:9.1":"“Kivaciram nu me yakkha, ","ja439:9.2":"cakkam sirasi thassati; ","ja439:9.3":"Kati vassasahassani, ","ja439:9.4":"tam me akkhahi pucchito”. ","ja439:10.1":"“Atisaro paccasaro, ","ja439:10.2":"mittavinda sunohi me; ","ja439:10.3":"Cakkam te sirasi maviddham, ","ja439:10.4":"na tam jivam pamokkhasi”ti. ","ja439:11.1":"Catudvarajatakam pathamam. "}